Name: Breach Rate Quartile Band
Expression:
VAR _Rank = RANKX(ALLSELECTED('A&E_Quarterly'), [Breach Rate], , ASC, Dense)
VAR _Total = COUNTROWS(ALLSELECTED('A&E_Quarterly'))
RETURN
    SWITCH(
        TRUE(),
        _Rank <= _Total / 4, "Top Quartile",
        _Rank <= _Total / 2, "2nd Quartile",
        _Rank <= _Total * 3/4, "3rd Quartile",
        "Bottom Quartile"
    )

Name: Breach Rate Z-Score
Expression:
VAR _Avg = AVERAGEX(ALL('A&E_Quarterly'), [Breach Rate])
VAR _StDev = STDEVX.P(ALL('A&E_Quarterly'), [Breach Rate])
RETURN
    DIVIDE(([Breach Rate] - _Avg), _StDev)

Name: Avg_BreachRate_PreviousQuarter
Expression:
VAR CurrentYear = MAX('A&E_Quarterly'[Corrected Year])
VAR CurrentQuarter = MAX('A&E_Quarterly'[Quarter])

VAR PrevQuarter = IF(CurrentQuarter = 1, 4, CurrentQuarter - 1)
VAR PrevYear = IF(CurrentQuarter = 1, CurrentYear - 1, CurrentYear)

RETURN
CALCULATE(
    AVERAGE('A&E_Quarterly'[breach_rate]),
    'A&E_Quarterly'[Corrected Year] = PrevYear,
    'A&E_Quarterly'[Quarter] = PrevQuarter
)

Name: Previous Breach Rate
Expression:
VAR CurrentYear = SELECTEDVALUE('A&E_Quarterly'[Corrected Year])
VAR CurrentQuarter = SELECTEDVALUE('A&E_Quarterly'[Quarter])

VAR PrevQuarter = IF(CurrentQuarter = 1, 4, CurrentQuarter - 1)
VAR PrevYear = IF(CurrentQuarter = 1, CurrentYear - 1, CurrentYear)

RETURN
CALCULATE(
    AVERAGE('A&E_Quarterly'[breach_rate]),
    'A&E_Quarterly'[Corrected Year] = PrevYear,
    'A&E_Quarterly'[Quarter] = PrevQuarter,
    ALLEXCEPT('A&E_Quarterly', 'A&E_Quarterly'[Trust_Code])
)

Name: DimDate_IsUnique
Expression:
VAR d =
    SUMX (
        SUMMARIZE ( DimDate1, DimDate1[Trust_Quarter_ID] ),
        1
    )
RETURN
d = DISTINCTCOUNT ( DimDate1[Trust_Quarter_ID] )
